### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Generate SQL - Simple
POST http://localhost:8000/generate-sql
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "question": "How many employees are there?",
    "schema": "Database: company\nTables: employees (id, name, department, salary)"
}

### Generate SQL - Complex
POST http://localhost:8000/generate-sql
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "question": "What is the average salary by department?",
    "schema": "Database: hr\nTables: employees (id, name, department, salary, hire_date)"
}

### Get Examples
GET http://localhost:8000/examples